="0:22.860">I</span> <span begin="0:22.860" end="0:23.218">got</span> <span begin="0:23.218" end="0:23.565">a</span> <span begin="0:23.565" end="0:24.189">ring</span> <span begin="0:24.545" end="0:25.828">因为幸福</span><span begin="0:25.828" end="0:26.530">喜</span><span begin="0:26.530" end="0:27.181">极而</span><span begin="0:27.181" end="0:27.650">泣</span></p><p begin="0:27.869" end="0:36.085" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="0:27.869" end="0:28.589">答应</span><span begin="0:28.589" end="0:28.974">你</span> <span begin="0:29.263" end="0:29.906">从今</span><span begin="0:29.906" end="0:30.329">起</span> <span begin="0:30.609" end="0:31.289">做你</span><span begin="0:31.289" end="0:31.949">的</span><span begin="0:31.949" end="0:33.964">妻和你永不分</span><span begin="0:33.964" end="0:36.085">离</span></p></div><div begin="0:34.655" end="1:17.898" itunes:songPart="Verse"><p begin="0:34.655" end="0:37.138" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:34.655" end="0:36.698">已经很难动心在我这样的年</span><span begin="0:36.698" end="0:37.138">纪</span></p><p begin="0:37.273" end="0:39.820" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:37.273" end="0:39.396">有时会回避也有时候逢场作</span><span begin="0:39.396" end="0:39.820">戏</span></p><p begin="0:39.912" end="0:42.429" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:39.912" end="0:40.732">成年人的默</span><span begin="0:40.732" end="0:41.076">契</span> <span begin="0:41.253" end="0:42.089">酒精麻痹过</span><span begin="0:42.089" end="0:42.429">去</span></p><p begin="0:42.626" end="0:45.151" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:42.626" end="0:44.799">经历了几段情让一颗心慢慢封</span><span begin="0:44.799" end="0:45.151">闭</span></p><p begin="0:45.315" end="0:47.944" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:45.315" end="0:47.689">也许这正是天意老天让我遇见了</span><span begin="0:47.689" end="0:47.944">你</span></p><p begin="0:48.006" end="0:50.609" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:48.006" end="0:50.364">像一只春天的小鹿撞进了我的怀</span><span begin="0:50.364" end="0:50.609">里</span></p><p begin="0:50.703" end="0:53.369" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:50.703" end="0:51.707">夏日海风的热</span><span begin="0:51.707" end="0:51.914">情</span> <span begin="0:52.064" end="0:53.082">融化了我这块</span><span begin="0:53.082" end="0:53.369">冰</span></p><p begin="0:53.437" end="0:55.999" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:53.437" end="0:55.758">冬季柔软的围巾天冷了会把我抱</span><span begin="0:55.758" end="0:55.999">紧</span></p><p begin="0:56.106" end="0:58.741" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:56.106" end="0:57.101">幸运却害怕失</span><span begin="0:57.101" end="0:57.334">去</span> <span begin="0:57.454" end="0:58.466">对爱情不再相</span><span begin="0:58.466" end="0:58.741">信</span></p><p begin="0:58.805" end="1:01.413" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:58.805" end="0:59.822">你触摸我的犹</span><span begin="0:59.822" end="1:00.021">豫</span> <span begin="1:00.150" end="1:01.168">你抚慰我的忧</span><span begin="1:01.168" end="1:01.413">郁</span></p><p begin="1:01.522" end="1:04.074" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:01.522" end="1:02.513">曾经我心如灰</span><span begin="1:02.513" end="1:02.679">烬</span> <span begin="1:02.846" end="1:03.873">却因你泛起涟</span><span begin="1:03.873" end="1:04.074">漪</span></p><p begin="1:04.194" end="1:06.791" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:04.194" end="1:06.538">从那一刻你吻我趁我还来不及反</span><span begin="1:06.538" end="1:06.791">应</span></p><p begin="1:06.938" end="1:09.639" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:06.938" end="1:09.426">每当我慢慢的靠近鼻翼或脸颊的回</span><span begin="1:09.426" end="1:09.639">应</span></p><p begin="1:09.777" end="1:12.375" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:09.777" end="1:10.923">当我越来越接近</span> <span begin="1:10.923" end="1:12.090">你眼神如此的肯</span><span begin="1:12.090" end="1:12.375">定</span></p><p begin="1:12.439" end="1:15.130" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:12.439" end="1:13.425">将你捧在我掌</span><span begin="1:13.425" end="1:13.644">心</span> <span begin=