egin="1:35.981" end="1:36.648">的</span><span begin="1:36.648" end="1:38.679">妻和你永不分</span><span begin="1:38.679" end="1:40.819">离</span></p></div><div begin="1:39.176" end="2:43.069" itunes:songPart="Verse"><p begin="1:39.176" end="1:41.718" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:39.176" end="1:40.217">习惯亲吻你额</span><span begin="1:40.217" end="1:40.468">头</span> <span begin="1:40.585" end="1:40.768">习</span><span begin="1:40.768" end="1:40.968">惯</span><span begin="1:40.968" end="1:41.077">了</span><span begin="1:41.077" end="1:41.417">牵着</span><span begin="1:41.417" end="1:41.718">手</span></p><p begin="1:41.934" end="1:44.451" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:41.934" end="1:42.908">习惯了互相依</span><span begin="1:42.908" end="1:43.146">靠</span> <span begin="1:43.295" end="1:43.795">月光下</span><span begin="1:43.795" end="1:43.994">慢</span><span begin="1:43.994" end="1:44.132">慢</span><span begin="1:44.132" end="1:44.451">走</span></p><p begin="1:44.635" end="1:47.208" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:44.635" end="1:45.630">有你的日子之</span><span begin="1:45.630" end="1:45.862">后</span> <span begin="1:46.001" end="1:46.477">我不再</span><span begin="1:46.477" end="1:46.674">出</span><span begin="1:46.674" end="1:46.807">去</span><span begin="1:46.807" end="1:46.982">喝</span><span begin="1:46.982" end="1:47.208">酒</span></p><p begin="1:47.347" end="1:49.955" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:47.347" end="1:48.331">我学会珍惜感</span><span begin="1:48.331" end="1:48.611">情</span> <span begin="1:48.672" end="1:49.219">学会感</span><span begin="1:49.219" end="1:49.400">恩</span><span begin="1:49.400" end="1:49.530">这</span><span begin="1:49.530" end="1:49.712">所</span><span begin="1:49.712" end="1:49.955">有</span></p><p begin="1:50.056" end="1:52.640" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:50.056" end="1:52.356">春天公园的小路看着樱花散步回</span><span begin="1:52.356" end="1:52.640">家</span></p><p begin="1:52.721" end="1:55.329" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:52.721" end="1:55.109">夏日清凉的午夜试着帮你吹干头</span><span begin="1:55.109" end="1:55.329">发</span></p><p begin="1:55.436" end="1:58.074" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:55.436" end="1:56.423">冬天你泡着热</span><span begin="1:56.423" end="1:56.681">茶</span> <span begin="1:56.771" end="1:57.786">我陪你窝在沙</span><span begin="1:57.786" end="1:58.074">发</span></p><p begin="1:58.204" end="2:00.721" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:58.204" end="1:59.967">相濡以沫成了彼此生命</span><span begin="1:59.967" end="2:00.167">中</span><span begin="2:00.167" end="2:00.301">的</span><span begin="2:00.301" end="2:00.485">牵</span><span begin="2:00.485" end="2:00.721">挂</span></p><p begin="2:00.903" end="2:03.558" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:00.903" end="2:01.658">何德何能</span> <span begin="2:01.658" end="2:03.321">我能拥有如此温柔的女</span><span begin="2:03.321" end="2:03.558">人</span></p><p begin="2:03.646" end="2:06.304" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:03.646" end="2:06.041">在最低沉的时候陪伴我让我再启</span><span begin="2:06.041" end="2:06.304">程</span></p><p begin="2:06.396" end="2:08.893" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:06.396" end="2:08.734">用你最好的青春安慰我躁郁的灵</span><span begin="2:08.734" end="2:08.893">魂</span></p><p begin="2:08.895" end="2:11.647" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:08.895" end="2:11.231">一颗心渐渐地安稳因为你一次次</span><span begin="2:11.231" end="2:11.367">包</span><span begin="2:11.367" end="2:11.647">容</span></p><p begin="2:11.762" end="2:13.573" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:11.762" end="2:11.963">Oh</span> <span begin="2:11.963" end="2:12.138">my</span> <span begin="2:12.138" end="2:12.373">babe</span> <span begin="2:12.447" end="2:13.277">对你说声感</span><span begin="2:13.277" end="2:13.573">谢</span></p><p begin="2:13.770" end="2:16.317" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:13.770" end="2:14.137">有了</span><span begin="2:14.137" end="2:14.357">你</span> <span begin="2:14.615" end="2:15.976">